{"tid":1209493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有感而發] 今次成件事連登都完勝高登","createTime":"2019-06-12T11:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T12:37:51.000Z","uid":59440,"like":151,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3711d4ecd933e979fd00c20728e076c2eb148279","tid":1209493,"uid":59440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7067298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D7067298&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=b85ebe44\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7067298</a><br />\n屌你高登612真係罷工，淨係出個公告係到跟風罷工呃like，身為網絡媒體唔係應該留守係到mon住個平台咩？<br />\n你罷工咁由得啲三毛係到妖言惑眾？咁大間公司用下腦啦，唔通報館記者又罷工？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202856/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202856/page/1</a><br />\n連登起碼唔會一味盲目跟風，而係做實事收起廣告真正響應罷工行動，緊守崗位睇實有冇人攻擊server或者搞事，幫大家報導最新情況<br />\n<br />\n高登？你罷條毛咩，咪又係un un腳袋廣告錢，罷到咁撚肉酸<br />\nOK！就當冇人上你個爛鬼forum，唔洗睇實<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9o0kaYW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9o0kaYW.png&h=dccb4d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但你連fb page都罷工，你咁撚多人follow，你唔係應該好好善用佢來為大家跟進時事架咩？<br />\n唔係有高登記者架咩？八掛新聞跟到咁足，今次咁大單野就唔報？<br />\n屌你真係完全唔撚po任何野，衰撚過达哥<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lihkg.forum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flihkg.forum&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=ac8e3c40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lihkg.forum</a><br />\n連登fb雖然冇高登咁多人follow，但起碼會同大家跟進同報導最新情況，哩三日來不斷係咁出有關逃犯條例fb post 就咁數都差唔多有30幾個po<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>高登真係冇得救架啦，連仔唔該你繼續keep住搞好連登<br />\n唔好辜負我地一班巴絲咁撐你</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a035c6c02965e8386